{"tid":981103,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[新地] 回顧學友出道早期俊秀相　稚氣變成熟男人 😁","createTime":"2019-01-14T04:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T09:56:46.000Z","uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2fef983cdc20cbf900bcf5f843ca897c8c52cd","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"｜85年 可愛單眼皮<br />\n<br />\n贏得《 十八區業餘歌唱大賽 》冠軍後，85年首張大碟《 Smile 》大賣20萬張 ( 四白金 )，瞬間成炙手可熱新晉歌手，當年24歲嘅學友一臉稚氣係個可愛單眼皮男孩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/egf_6731909035c3869ec98d51-1050x1387.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fegf_6731909035c3869ec98d51-1050x1387.jpg&h=e4378183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5421f8cd3ce1ea0682b9c12105714be459e4dcea","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"｜86年 擘髀型坐凳<br />\n<br />\n著上吊帶牛仔褲到球場影相，左手撐腰擘髀坐凳，坐姿有型，而佢件闊到衣不稱身嘅 上衣，打扮受日本八十年代潮服影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1101a_sundaytreasure_p44_45_g_8660774335c386a45d6e11-1050x1524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F1101a_sundaytreasure_p44_45_g_8660774335c386a45d6e11-1050x1524.jpg&h=daefafe3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f6e1dec825c2f4574a4e50b4d4c552b7ba69c9a","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"｜86年 生日會獻唱<br />\n<br />\n某 disco 舉行25歲生日會，除經理人陳自強、成龍、張國榮、張衞健等圈中人出席外，仲有近六百位歌迷，場面墟冚，難怪獻唱時特別興奮開心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vw_1916676715c386aa86b67d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fvw_1916676715c386aa86b67d.jpg&h=e289f9b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8c8ee58e90d66904e5396c645904b3e416be99b","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"｜86年 單手拉彈弓<br />\n<br />\n登上某音樂雜誌封面，喺跨頁海報人物中著運動褲坐喺地單手玩拉彈弓，學友歌聲雄渾，原來亦大力到暈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brwdv_6370009305c386ad7e6984-1050x1760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fbrwdv_6370009305c386ad7e6984-1050x1760.jpg&h=748ebe19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99c72437761750b5b2fd8ed3417dbbbd25cfc890","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"｜86年 情定羅美薇<br />\n<br />\n參演第二部電影《痴心的我》擔任男主角之一，同另一女主角羅美薇戲假情真撻著成為情侶，兩年拍拖十年喺倫敦註冊結婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/efdf_11843580875c386b25c9f29-1050x693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fefdf_11843580875c386b25c9f29-1050x693.jpg&h=fb9e6132&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b47f36c4e7a22e087f0904d658932a001499755a","tid":981103,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:31:39.000Z","msg":"佢割雙眼皮？"},{"pid":"325fce0ae8ab47e7a7633bc8893d10c547da3d6d","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:32:28.000Z","msg":"｜87年 罕著潛水衣<br />\n<br />\n除咗係樂壇天王，亦係運動健 將，尤其網球最精，87年罕有全副潛水裝上陣，展現無限活力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/v_3089858065c386b6bc8891-1050x1396.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fv_3089858065c386b6bc8891-1050x1396.jpg&h=6e294ad4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"692120d474217ddfca13b715463173c89f560e4d","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:32:59.000Z","msg":"｜88年 突變雙眼皮<br />\n<br />\n呢張攝於88年嘅相，發現未滿27歲嘅張學友由以往單眼皮突然變成雙眼皮，隨即惹嚟做割皮手術傳聞，據學友解釋話係慢慢自然變成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/gq_5051198365c386ba089a50-1050x1073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fgq_5051198365c386ba089a50-1050x1073.jpg&h=f86028f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35904ff654bc6611958f169df0ed7a6d349f878b","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"｜89年 騎呢笠雀籠<br />\n<br />\n替某音樂雜誌影相，應攝影師要求，滿頸圍住多個雀籠，騎呢程度媲美 譚小環 CD 封面頭笠雀籠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ef_11815110645c386bd1a5a73-1050x1677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fef_11815110645c386bd1a5a73-1050x1677.jpg&h=30214471&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca7e22ba592309cef45797ccd06784de994f220f","tid":981103,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:33:36.000Z","msg":"實力派硬係要行偶像派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48101dc5db612a73fef176a1492674a923e94c9","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"｜89年 最佳男配角<br />\n<br />\n電影代表作係88年嘅《旺角卡 門 》，片中演劉德華條𡃁烏蠅，衝動又惹人煩厭，「 寧願做一日英雄，都唔要做一世烏蠅 」成金句，翌年憑烏蠅一角奪第8屆香港電影金像獎「 最佳男配角 」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/rbvf_17141027565c386c05c1697-1050x644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Frbvf_17141027565c386c05c1697-1050x644.jpg&h=b5f5f766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8d259ecca1a3dea73af26031ecc76bd358bd4b5","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:34:00.000Z","msg":"｜92年 孖梅姐致敬<br />\n<br />\n92年「初代歌神」許冠傑宣布退休，無綫舉行《 許冠傑光榮引退匯群星 》，全港當紅歌手同影星出席，場面史無前例，有份上台獻唱致敬嘅天王張學友同天后梅艶芳喺席上合照留念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/efa_156811705c386c9109eaa-1050x1220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fefa_156811705c386c9109eaa-1050x1220.jpg&h=6258e4fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7cdb1d9f798f588252a5bb0ea3c62b9a925eb9d","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"｜93年 穿粵紅線女<br />\n<br />\n93年香港電台同廣東電台為「 希望工程 」 籌款製作《 萬千希望在人間 》，天王張學友夥拍粵劇名伶紅線女合演折子戲〈 初遇訴情 〉，一個係樂壇歌神，一個係粵劇泰斗，破天荒跨界合作成一時佳話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/efd_3604668375c386c56804db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fefd_3604668375c386c56804db.jpg&h=5169adb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"377658ac55925c02ad96a6aebc1708d9089edaae","tid":981103,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"型"},{"pid":"cebbcc5ecb828b4e05b31082e46f6137523985dc","tid":981103,"uid":7015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b48101dc5db612a73fef176a1492674a923e94c9","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"｜89年 最佳男配角<br />\n<br />\n電影代表作係88年嘅《旺角卡 門 》，片中演劉德華條𡃁烏蠅，衝動又惹人煩厭，「 寧願做一日英雄，都唔要做一世烏蠅 」成金句，翌年憑烏蠅一角奪第8屆香港電影金像獎「 最佳男配角 」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/rbvf_17141027565c386c05c1697-1050x644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Frbvf_17141027565c386c05c1697-1050x644.jpg&h=b5f5f766&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"金句應該係「食屎啦你」？"},{"pid":"d012309f753561c5f55c5845db64c9285b9aedca","tid":981103,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"Me=美薇"},{"pid":"a4a3d210bc41465503c2069c77f42430f4d2a19f","tid":981103,"uid":176368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"今時今日睇割雙眼皮有咩大不了"},{"pid":"4b43b2ddb9de960c6315afec7800db02450defeb","tid":981103,"uid":55523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"第一張相好似表哥"},{"pid":"0c3abd855ad0eba0e9482fd7f05f82f674cb7d12","tid":981103,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:48:08.000Z","msg":"我愛黎明"},{"pid":"b6ab6b9d7aff77cda1dc3cda2f6ddd48bb790e24","tid":981103,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d012309f753561c5f55c5845db64c9285b9aedca","tid":981103,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"Me=美薇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:49:03.000Z","msg":"你=癲婆"},{"pid":"71e61416f88f8122b3e601d0cc6d33b29b1367d7","tid":981103,"uid":60558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"第一張相咁似JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146f905d8e38954f694c3295e6fe938f1021898f","tid":981103,"uid":77186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"無割 邊會信"},{"pid":"db931b4ae44640273610ee1edac472b993892f41","tid":981103,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"692120d474217ddfca13b715463173c89f560e4d","tid":981103,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:32:59.000Z","msg":"｜88年 突變雙眼皮<br />\n<br />\n呢張攝於88年嘅相，發現未滿27歲嘅張學友由以往單眼皮突然變成雙眼皮，隨即惹嚟做割皮手術傳聞，據學友解釋話係慢慢自然變成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/gq_5051198365c386ba089a50-1050x1073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fgq_5051198365c386ba089a50-1050x1073.jpg&h=f86028f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"以前d技術都唔錯"},{"pid":"6adbebfd126307057b2413abb9ee95ad234918b6","tid":981103,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b43b2ddb9de960c6315afec7800db02450defeb","tid":981103,"uid":55523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"第一張相好似表哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:51:28.000Z","msg":"似鄭中基"},{"pid":"ab0fa4bd455ea51d0335f5d96c43d304f1105604","tid":981103,"uid":170979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"146f905d8e38954f694c3295e6fe938f1021898f","tid":981103,"uid":77186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"無割 邊會信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"其實睇返佢87-89年代舊電影已時單時雙<br />\n佢係猛鬼差館入面已經係一時單  轉個場景又變雙 <br />\n有睇過佢舊電影既人會知<br />\n當然咁都唔代表佢冇微調既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但佢以前眼皮時單時雙一定係事實<br />\n<br />\n利伸：睇哂佢所有電影"}]}